    "description": "The Manage Subscriptions API enables businesses to efficiently handle subscription offerings and user sign-ups. This API allows service providers to create and manage subscriptions for their customers, ensuring seamless integration with billing systems and user management. Common use cases include onboarding new users, managing subscription plans, and updating subscription details. Ideal for developers building customer engagement platforms and recurring billing solutions.",
